"a :guilabel:`Configurazione`. Nel campo :guilabel:`Trunk vocale in entrata`, "
"seleziona :guilabel:`phone.systems`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:67
msgid "Odoo setup"
msgstr "Configurare Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/didww.rst:69
msgid ""
"In *Odoo*, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Integrations --> "
